{"ID":"20260605151109-wx3tm6a","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260605151109-wx3tm6a","title":"2021年浙江卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260605151125-ob6hq2o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151125-ob6hq2o","updated":"20260605151125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"意难忘·山家"}]},{"ID":"20260605151125-adx9jim","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151125-adx9jim","updated":"20260605151125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"[清]   吴伟业"}]},{"ID":"20260605151125-0o3ja2x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151125-0o3ja2x","updated":"20260605151125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"村坞云遮，有苍藤老干，翠竹明沙。溪堂连石稳，苔径逐篱斜。文木几，小窗纱，是好事人家。启北扉，移床待客，百树梅花。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151125-v9seuu5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151125-v9seuu5","updated":"20260605151125"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"衰翁健饭堪夸。把瘿尊①茗碗，高话桑麻。穿池还种柳，汲水自浇瓜。霜后橘，雨前茶，这风味清佳。喜去年，山田大熟，烂熳生涯。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151140-hl2wt07","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151140-hl2wt07","updated":"20260605151141"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"【注】①瘿尊，即瘿樽 用瘿瘤状木根所制的酒杯。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151109-hhixccg","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151109-hhixccg","updated":"20260605151158"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260605151158-5lhee2d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151158-5lhee2d","updated":"20260605151158"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．词中“衰翁”的身份是"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。下片中“"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"”一词点出山家的生活状态，可谓词眼。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151158-gq6m6ir","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151158-gq6m6ir","updated":"20260605151158"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．分别赏析上片的写景艺术和下片的叙事艺术。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151109-z63l0jb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151109-z63l0jb","updated":"20260605151212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260605151212-p7os3qc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151212-p7os3qc","updated":"20260605151212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．     隐士（农夫）     烂漫    20．写景艺术：①由远及近，由外到内。从村坞、山家到室内，步移景换。②意象丰密，色彩和谐。“苍藤老干”“翠竹明沙”，构成明净清幽之境。③以动写静，动静结合。如“苔径逐篱斜”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151212-zcxq667","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151212-zcxq667","updated":"20260605151212"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"叙事艺术：①对比衬托。如“蓑翁”与“健饭”。②铺陈写实。如“高话”以下，一一叙写山家生活。③以农家话语写自适情态。如“汲水自浇瓜”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151109-w0mnfw0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260605151109-w0mnfw0","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-h8upju2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-h8upju2","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查学生理解诗歌内容，鉴赏诗歌诗眼的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-teltpld","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-teltpld","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上阕写衰翁的居住环境在山野，室内陈设着文木制作的几案，小巧的窗户饰着纱，说明主人虽在山野也十分讲究，让人感到他是个富于生活情趣的雅士，故可推知其为隐士；下阕写衰翁话桑麻、种柳浇地，也可理解是为农夫。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-b17rvt0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-b17rvt0","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下阕 写衰翁待客，写了席间主客欢洽之情，啜茶饮酒，高话桑麻，去年自己耕种的山田收成极好，可以无忧无虑乐陶陶地过舒心日子了。生活丰富多彩，状态极佳。故能表现这一状态的词应为“烂漫”。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-wj3y4nr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-wj3y4nr","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20．本题考查学生鉴赏诗歌表达技巧的能力。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-4a5vz0g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-4a5vz0g","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"诗歌上阕写景。由步行向山家时沿途所见落笔。首句“村坞云遮”写由下仰望山上，人家村落在白云缭绕中依约可见。渐行渐近，写看到一幢房子，小径沿着篱笆斜伸过去，最后再到室内的陈设。词的上片由远及近、由外到内，移步换景的手法写景；"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-wn4b02r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-wn4b02r","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"房子依水傍石，稳稳地临溪而立，小径生满青苔，接着两句是写稍近些看到的老树上缠绕着青青的藤蔓，翠绿的修竹映衬着溪边的白沙，色彩鲜明可爱。用白描之笔富有层次地描绘了山家四周的环境和景物。描绘了隐士山家的幽静环境；"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-mwawv7k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-mwawv7k","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“苔径逐篱斜”，小径沿着篱笆斜伸过去，“逐”字化静为动；“文木几，小窗纱”“启北扉，移床待客”动静结合，表现农家生活的意趣，衬托出主人潇洒出尘的品格。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-3dygixx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-3dygixx","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下片写席间主客欢洽之情。隐士是个苍老体弱的衰翁，却出人意外地饮食健胜。作者用“衰翁健饭堪夸”一句来表示自己的惊奇，“衰翁”与“健饭”形成非常有趣的对比。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-8n6r1kt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-8n6r1kt","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"老人十分健谈，边啜茶饮酒，边兴致勃勃地谈起了农事。“把瘿尊茗碗，高话桑麻。穿池还种柳，汲水自浇瓜。霜后橘，雨前茶。这风味清佳”，一一罗列叙写田家生活及农事，为铺陈写实的手法。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151228-moxts79","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151228-moxts79","updated":"20260605151228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“穿池还种柳”是说在池边开沟引水，并种上柳树，与下面“汲水自浇瓜”都是老翁的农活。这两句以农家话语写老农的悠游轻松，让人羡慕隐逸生活的闲适。“这风味清佳”！ 这一句赞语非常口语化，老翁怡然而乐的神情跃然纸上。"}]},{"ID":"20260605151109-6r5gtn0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260605151109-6r5gtn0","updated":"20260605142207"}}]}